  "Ex04CrownRegression"}]], "Input",
 CellLabel->"In[15]:=",ExpressionUUID->"08589035-cc43-4269-bdcb-31ef479c8a43"],

Cell[BoxData[
 RowBox[{"hrfEx04InspectPolynomialScan", "[", 
  RowBox[{
  "Ex04CrownRegression", ",", "Automatic", ",", "Automatic", ",", 
   "KinAssump4ptOnShell", ",", "KinVars4pt", ",", 
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{"CrownData", "[", "\"\<UF\>\"", "]"}], "[", "\"\<U\>\"", "]"}]}], 
  "]"}]], "Input",
 CellLabel->"In[16]:=",ExpressionUUID->"79856b04-3835-4d49-8321-d493ca150bca"],

Cell["\<\
HyperCrown boundary {x11}=0 (WideAngle4ptBoundary: PairSectors, kin-free \
sector check). Obstruction ~1\[AHat]\.80\.933 min; coverage LP on 11 vars \
adds ~1\[AHat]\.80\.932 min. Assign the report, then pull copy-paste-friendly \
ingredients from the Association (not from Dataset cells).\
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"156e69ab-c144-4f57-9a3a-a1504f8c59a1"],

Cell[BoxData[
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{"hrfX11Report", "=", 
   RowBox[{"hrfEx04HyperCrownX11Display", "[", "]"}]}], ";"}]], "Input",
 CellLabel->"In[17]:=",ExpressionUUID->"e537a175-153e-4255-b67b-dfe126015ff2"],

Cell["\<\
Summary Dataset (display only). For generators, scaling vector, variable \
scaling use Ingredients below.\
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"e0d7b368-7774-491e-a2f9-45e425afc070"],

Cell[BoxData[
 RowBox[{"hrfX11Report", "[", "\"\<Summary\>\"", "]"}]], "Input",
 CellLabel->
  "In[17a]:=",ExpressionUUID->"f989b8da-c09d-4b73-9cad-e56a5a25f31c"],

Cell["\<\
Copy-paste friendly primary ingredients (same fields as summary row, as plain \
lists/associations):\
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"ef5f5635-c46c-4db4-8463-00a5ab12ac3f"],

Cell[BoxData[
 RowBox[{"KeyTake", "[", 
  RowBox[{
   RowBox[{"hrfX11Report", "[", "\"\<Ingredients\>\"", "]"}], ",", 
   RowBox[{"{", 
    RowBox[{
    "\"\<Generators\>\"", ",", "\"\<ScalingVector\>\"", ",", 
     "\"\<VariableScaling\>\""}], "}"}]}], "]"}]], "Input",
 CellLabel->
  "In[17b]:=",ExpressionUUID->"418958de-fd49-4aa7-aed4-1dc4c11b1bdd"],

Cell["\<\
Per-trial tables include Scaling vector and Variable scaling columns. Full \
structured log: hrfX11Report[\"Extract\"].\
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"3f3e413f-f478-48ac-8f13-b275adcddad4"],

Cell[BoxData[
 RowBox[{"hrfX11Report", "[", "\"\<AllValidTrialsScaling\>\"", "]"}]], "Input",\

 CellLabel->
  "In[17c]:=",ExpressionUUID->"73e5c28e-ec90-48b2-a847-776f133b899a"],

Cell["\<\
Per-trial audit (generators, sector form, decomposition, scaling). Re-scan \
without LP: Get[\"HRF_WideAngleBoundaryDiagnostic.wl\"]; \
hrfWideAngleBoundaryDiagnostic[\"HyperCrownX11\"]. With LP on valid trials \
only: add \"RunScalingQ\" -> True. Analyze existing scan: \
hrfWideAngleBoundaryDiagnosticFromScan[Ex04HyperCrownX11Target[\"\
PolynomialScan\"], ...].\
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"6dc7df6c-c368-4bb0-9f5a-e2a01bd8d808"],

Cell[BoxData[
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{"Get", "[", 
   RowBox[{"FileNameJoin", "[", 
    RowBox[{"{", 
     RowBox[{
      RowBox[{"NotebookDirectory", "[", "]"}], ",", 
      "\"\<HRF_WideAngleBoundaryDiagnostic.wl\>\""}], "}"}], "]"}], "]"}], 
  ";", 
  RowBox[{
   RowBox[{"hrfWideAngleBoundaryDiagnostic", "[", 
    RowBox[{"\"\<HyperCrownX11\>\"", ",", 
     RowBox[{"\"\<RunScalingQ\>\"", "\[Rule]", "False"}]}], "]"}], 
   "\[LeftDoubleBracket]", "1", "\[RightDoubleBracket]"}]}]], "Input",
 CellLabel->"In[18]:=",ExpressionUUID->"aeb51a96-3036-454f-8751-14c40f0232ba"],

Cell[BoxData[
 RowBox[{"hrfEx04InspectPolynomialScan", "[", 
  RowBox[{
  "Ex04HyperCrownX11Target", ",", "Automatic", ",", "Automatic", ",", 
   "KinAssump4ptOnShell", ",", "KinVars4pt", ",", 
   RowBox[{"Expand", "[", 
    RowBox[{
     RowBox[{
      RowBox[{"HyperCrownData", "[", "\"\<UF\>\"", "]"}], "[", "\"\<U\>\"", 
      "]"}], "/.", "\[VeryThinSpace]", 
     RowBox[{"x11", "\[Rule]", "0"}]}], "]"}]}], "]"}]], "Input",
 CellLabel->"In[18]:=",ExpressionUUID->"c4fce8ab-34d6-4c06-aac6-333221cf3b0e"],

Cell["\<\
OPTIONAL \[AHat]\.80\.94 HyperCrown interior (polynomial; ~5-15 min with \
trim). After In[19], check hrfHyperCrownInteriorNarrative[] for an exhaustive \
no-HR certificate. Full trial log: $HRFEx04TrimScanStorageQ=False and \
$HRFFindObstructionsStoreAllTrialsQ=True.\
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"c76e2aa3-286c-43ab-ac28-a2bfa8ec640b"],

